column5: Man O man there are some great deals to be had there! Ran into a few people from here and Phil and Hirk both have a table set up so if you go say 'hi' to them. It's still going on till 3PM so if you need soft plastics GET THERE!  Great deals on Rod's too!
Agreed this was worth my trip...great deals and a good bunch of guys.
Sounds like GBW scored on some free or near free stuff...
Wish we had something like that around here.
